TextEng: Farewell.
You don't agree with some people's methods of helping?
Text: 일부 사람들이 돕는 방식에 동의하지 않는 건가?

TextEng: How bad is it getting in this district?
Text: 이 지구 상황이 얼마나 나빠지고 있지?

TextEng: So who would you trust? Where is the safest place?
Text: 그럼 누구를 믿어야 하지? 가장 안전한 곳은 어디지?

TextEng: You lost a guard? Who was it?
You lose a man? But aren't they big?
Text: 사람 잃어버렸어? 근데 큰 사람들 아니야?

TextEng: So who you trust then? Where safest place?
Text: 그럼 누구 믿어? 제일 안전한 데 어디?

TextEng: This district really that bad?
You not think some people help good enough?
Text: 몇몇 사람들 돕는 거 별로라 생각해?

TextEng: I go now. Bye.
Are there any safe locations?
Any safe places?
Where did you see him last?
Where he last go?
Is there a reason for the undead infestation?
You know why undead now everywhere?
Have you heard anything about Waterdhavian creatures?
Text: 워터딥의 생명체들에 대해 들은 게 있나?

TextEng: You hear anything about Waterdhavi-whasis creature things?
Back to my previous questions.
Back to other questions, okay?
It was a Yuan-Ti named Gulnan who caused it all.
Text: 모든 걸 일으킨 건 굴난이라는 유안티였다.

TextEng: Snake lady Gulnan cause dead to walk and stuff.
Text: 뱀 아줌마 굴난이 죽은 자들 걸어 다니게 만들고 그랬어.

TextEng: The Beggar's Nest should be fine now.
Beggar's Nest all safe now.
Goodbye.
Bye bye thens.
